VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT InitialDirContext|InitialLdapContext|DirContext\.search\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:request|getParameter|getHeader|query|input && MISSING:escapeLDAPSearchFilter|ESAPI\.encoder\(\)\.encodeForLDAP|ldapEscape
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects LDAP context or search operations that may incorporate unescaped user input.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for LDAP Injection: InitialDirContext Search with User Input.
